text: Nasib Si Labu Labi (English: The Fate of Labu and Labi), also known as What Happened to Labu and Labi, is a 1963 Malay-language comedy film from Singapore. It is directed by and stars P. Ramlee. The movie is a sequel to Labu dan Labi and features many of the same actors. ==Cast== * P. Ramlee as Labi * M. Zain as Labu * Mariani as Manisah * Udo Omar as Haji Bakhil * S. Sudarmaji as Teacher Sudar * Habsah Buang as Headmistress * Murni Sarawak as Teacher Murni * S. Shamsuddin as Boxing Club Coach * Ibrahim Pendek as Murni father's * Ahmad C as Ahmad * Aziz Sattar as Matchmaker * Ahmad Nisfu as the judge * Ahmad Mahmud as Beauty pageant judge 1 * Omar Rojik as Beauty pageant judge 2 * Rosnani Jamil as Beauty pageant judge 3 * Sarimah Ahmad as Beauty pageant judge 4 * Dayang Sofia as Beauty pageant judge 5 * Saloma as Singer at variety show ==Songs== * Barang Yang Lepas Jangan Dikenang (Don't Yearn For That Which is Gone) * Tarian Silat Orang Melayu (Malay Silat Dance) * Aci Aci Buka Pintu (Aci, Aci, Open the Door) ==Related pages== * P. Ramlee filmography ==References== ==Other websites== *
title: Nasib Si Labu Labi
